\c 4 
\m \bd Faarfannaa \bd*\bd 4\bd*
\s2 \bdit \zbr\bdit*Kadhata Galgalaa (Geggeessituu warra faarfatootaaf; kun mi'a ribuu qabuun faarfatame; faarfannaa Daawit)
\m \bd 1\bd* Yaa Waaqayyo isa dhugaa anaaf baaftuu, yeroon si waammadhu anaaf deebisi! Yeroo ani muddama keessa turetti, ati keessaa na baafteetta; ati araara anatti argisiisi! Kadhata koos anaaf dhaga'i.
\m \bd 2\bd* Yaa jarana, isin hamma yoomiitti ulfina koo salphiftu? Hamma yoomiitti dubbii waa'ee hin baafne jaallattu? Hamma yoomiittis soba faana dhooftu?
\m \bd 3\bd* Garuu Waaqayyo warra kan isaa ta'an, addaan akka baafate beekaa! Waaqayyo yeroo ani isa waammadhutti anaaf in dhaga'a.
\m \bd 4\bd* yoo aartan iyyuu, cubbuu hin hojjetinaa! Yeroo gab jettanii siree keessan irra jirtanitti, kana garaa keessanitti itti yaadaa! 
\m \bd 5\bd* Aarsaa isa qajeelaa dhi'eessaa! Waaqayyotti amanattaniis isatti dhiisaa.
\m \bd 6\bd* Namoonni baay'een, ''Eenyutu waan gaarii nutti argisiisa?'' in jedhu; yaa Waaqayyo, ati ifa fuula keetii nu irratti ol kaasi!
\m \bd 7\bd* Isa warri kaan midhaan isaanii fi daadhii waynii isaanii baay'ee irraa argatan caalaatti, ati gammachuu caalu garaa koof kenniteetta.
\m \bd 8\bd* Yaa Waaqayyo, akka ani qoofniitti sodaa malee jiraadhu situ godha; kanaafis ani akkuman ciiseen nagaatti nan rafa.
